{"tid":121212,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"【攞你命3000】科技原子筆　手機充電USB儲存觸控屏幕樣樣齊","createTime":"2017-02-15T05:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T05:18:40.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b25fb1672d6fcb926a59384a360ff1eb020ca69","tid":121212,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:09:58.000Z","msg":"【攞你命3000】科技原子筆　手機充電USB儲存觸控屏幕樣樣齊<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/tech/art/20170214/19927351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ftech%2Fart%2F20170214%2F19927351&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=6dcb3569\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ftech%2Fart%2F20170214%2F19927351&h=d18f7c9a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/tech/art/20170214/19927351</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170214/large/55ss01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170214%2Flarge%2F55ss01.jpg&h=a227db97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以為是一支原子筆？其實佢是集多項科技元素於一身的「攞你命3000」原子筆！正在Indiegogo集資的ChargeWrite可能都受到「聞西」啟發，將USB儲存（16GB）、外置電池（650mAh／1,000mAh）、屏幕清潔器、觸控筆加到ChargeWrite身上，而且筆頭更內置Lightning及Micro USB插頭，一插入iPhone或Android手機都可充電，但當然這支筆確實是一支筆，能夠作書寫功能。價錢最平都只是29美元（約$225），4月開始供貨，都算幾抵玩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170214/large/55ss02.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170214%2Flarge%2F55ss02.jpg&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=9e620d12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170214%2Flarge%2F55ss02.jpg&h=9cde8a22\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.appl